                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9702" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0329</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">748 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一心堂的危机与破局：连锁药店的管理反思</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Crisis and Breakthrough of Yixintang:  Management Reflections on Chain Drugstores</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">卢佳瑄，武鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南鸿翔一心堂药业(集团)股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业伦理；合规管理；危机管理；企业社会责任；医药零售行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business ethics; Compliance management; Crisis management; Social responsibility; Pharmaceutical retail industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在我国医药零售行业快速扩张的进程中，连锁药店通过规模化布局抢占市场红利，但跨区域管理复杂度攀升、合规风险交织等问题逐渐显现。头部企业因战略重心偏移与内控失效引发的系统性危机，不仅威胁企业发展，更折射出行业高速发展背后的治理隐患。本案例以国内连锁药店龙头企业一心堂为研究对象，以“崛起—危机—破局”为主线，全景式呈现其从区域性药材收购站成长为万店规模上市集团的扩张历程，重点聚焦2024年集中爆发的税务违规、医保套现、药品质量三重危机事件，深度剖析企业在快速扩张中累积的管理漏洞与伦理失范问题，并系统梳理其破局举措通过声誉修复、合规管理实现危机突围的实践路径。本案例旨在引导学生深入探讨医药零售企业在规模扩张与社会责任、商业效率与伦理底线间的动态平衡难题，理解多维度风险叠加传导的机理，掌握危机情境下的响应策略与长效合规治理逻辑。通过剖析行业标杆企业的危机事件，深化学生对商业伦理根基、社会责任履行与企业可持续发展的辩证认知，为医药零售行业转型升级提供理论参考与实践启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">During the rapid expansion of China&#39;s pharmaceutical retail industry, chain drugstores have seized market dividends through large-scale layout. However, problems such as increasing complexity in cross-regional management and intertwined compliance risks have gradually emerged. Systemic crises triggered by strategic focus shifts and internal control failures in leading enterprises not only threaten their development but also reflect governance risks hidden behind the industry&#39;s rapid development. This case study takes Yixintang, a leading domestic chain drugstore enterprise, as the research object, following the main thread of &quot;rise - crisis - breakthrough&quot;, presenting a panoramic view of its expansion journey from a regional herbal medicine acquisition station to a listed group with tens of thousands of stores. It focuses on the three major crisis events of tax violations, medical insurance fraud, and drug quality issues that erupted in 2024, deeply analyzing the management loopholes and ethical violations accumulated during its rapid expansion, and systematically sorting out its breakthrough measures, including reputation restoration and compliance management, to achieve crisis resolution. This case study aims to guide students to deeply explore the dynamic balance problem between scale expansion and social responsibility, business efficiency and ethical bottom line in pharmaceutical retail enterprises, understand the mechanism of multi-dimensional risk superposition and transmission, and master the response strategies and long-term compliance governance logic in crisis situations.By analyzing the crisis events of industry benchmark enterprises, it deepens students&#39; dialectical understanding of business model innovation, social responsibility fulfillment, and sustainable enterprise development, providing theoretical references and practical inspirations for the transformation and upgrading of the pharmaceutical retail industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》、《商业伦理与企业社会责任》、《商业伦理与会计职业道德》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业伦理决策模型；伦理失范风险；形象修复理论；4R危机管理理论；合规管理体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
